TY  - JOUR
TI  - An Analysis of the Properties of the Exact Finite Sample Distribution of a Nonconsistent GCL Structural Variance Estimator
AU  - Ebbeler, Donald H.
AU  - McDonald, James B.
AB  - [An asymptotic expansion of a confluent hypergeometric series is used to approximate the exact finite sample distribution function of a nonconsistent GCL structural variance estimator. A theoretical result is used to motivate the specification of a simple algorithm under which we may accept or reject the use of the asymptotic distribution function of the GCL estimator to approximate the exact distribution function.]
