TY  - JOUR
TI  - Approximations to the Distribution Functions of the Ordinary Least-Squares and Two-Stage Least-Squares Estimators in the Case of Two Included Endogenous Variables
AU  - Mariano, Roberto S.
AB  - [This paper deals with single-equation estimators in a simultaneous system of linear stochastic equations and approximates the distribution function of the two-stage least-squares estimators up to terms whose order of magnitude is <tex-math>$1/\sqrt{N}$</tex-math>, where N is the sample size. For fixed N, an approximation to the OLS distribution function is also obtained up to terms whose order of magnitude 1/μ, where μ <sup>2</sup> is what is referred to in the literature as the concentration parameter.]
