TI  - Restricted and Unrestricted Reduced Forms: Asymptotic Distribution and Relative Efficiency
AU  - Dhrymes, Phoebus J.
AB  - [This paper derives the asymptotic distribution of restricted and unrestricted reduced form estimators and compares their asymptotic efficiency. It also shows that the same techniques yield the asymptotic distribution of dynamic multipliers.]
